lies, on top of a better\nphysical description of correlated metals and insulators, a reduced occurrence\nof unphysical metastable solutions in correlated insulators in comparison to\nDFT+U.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jan 2011 15:21:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Jan 2013 14:10:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-24"}
